nd":"italic_en","text":"a shallow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eus~","text_ar":"عُسّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (so accord. to a copy of the S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bowl,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drinking-cup,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadaH","text_ar":"قَدَح"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is neither large nor small:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [now applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a plate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dish:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHunN","text_ar":"اَصْحُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, * TA) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiHaAnN","text_ar":"صِحَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) [and app., agreeably with modern usage,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHuwnN","text_ar":"صُحُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b2-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cymbal;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small brazen basin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TusayotN","text_ar":"طُسَيْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TasotN","text_ar":"طَسْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of what are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHonaAni","text_ar":"صَحْنَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) this meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two little brazen basins,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TusayotaAni SagiyrataAni","text_ar":"طُسَيْتَانِ صَغِيرَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which are struck together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S. K.) ―         -b3-  And (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior of the solid hoof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"skrjp","text_ar":"سكرجة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sukur~ujap","text_ar":"سُكُرُّجَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sukur~ajap","text_ar":"سُكُرَّجَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the ear: or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaArap","text_ar":"مَحَارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concha"},{"kind":"text","text":"] thereof. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHonaA AlA^u*unayoni","text_ar":"صَحْنَا الاُذُنَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[thus accord. to the TA and my MS. copy of the K, in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHonA'u","text_ar":"صَحْناءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The resting-place"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotaqar~","text_ar":"مُسْتَقَرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the interior of each of the ears;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place of hearing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meatus auditorius"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the resting-place of the interior of each of the two ears"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the horse: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHaAnN","text_ar":"اَصْحَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b5-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a house; (S, K;) meaning the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAHap","text_ar":"سَاحَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"court"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the middle"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a house [and of a mosque &c.]: (TA:) [and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for] it is thus called"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether without,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with, a roof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kull, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayotN","text_ar":"بَيْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAHap","text_ar":"سَاحَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spacious vacant part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the middle"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a desert; and of an elevated and plain, or hard and elevated, tract; and of a wide space of low, or depressed, ground: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHuwnN","text_ar":"صُحُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the only pl. form. (TA.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wide part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a desert: so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sironaA fiY SaHoni","text_ar":"سِرْنَا فِى صَحْنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfalaApi","text_ar":"الفَلَاةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We journeyed in the wide part of the desert"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A level,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plain, tract"},{"kind":"text","text":"of ground. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An acclivity"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanad","text_ar":"سَنَد"},{"kind":"text","text":") of a valley,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is some elevation above"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated ground, as though supported"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the latter"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and in like manner, of a mountain, and of a hill such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamap","text_ar":"اَكَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHuwn","text_ar":"صُحُون"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the ground being the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufuwf","text_ar":"دُفُوف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"banks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acclivities,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] thereof: it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bare, and such as flows"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with rain"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and is not thus called unless"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bare of everything, and even:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it means also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an even tract of ground like the area of the place in which dates are put to dry."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY Ald~amoEu EalaY SaHonaYo wajonatayohi","text_ar":"جَرَى الدَّمْعُ عَلَى صَحْنَىْ وَجْنَتَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tears ran upon the middle of each of his cheek-balls"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A gift."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See 1, first sentence.])"}],"source_refs":["TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}